---
// Game landing page for Static Run
---

<html>
  <head>
    <title>Static Run | ephergent.com</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@900&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #0a0a1a 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      .game-hero {
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        color: #0ff1ce;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .tagline {
        color: #0ff1ce;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff1ce44;
      }
      .nav-link {
        color: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #0ff1ce;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .nav-link:hover {
        background: #0ff1ce;
        color: #0a0a1a;
      }
      .game-card {
        background: rgba(10,16,32,0.8);
        border: 1px solid #0ff1ce33;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .specs {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .spec-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0ff1ce22;
      }
      .spec-label {
        color: #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .scanlines {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
        pointer-events: none;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          transparent, transparent 6px,
          #0ff1ce08 7px, transparent 8px
        );
        z-index: 10;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden p-8">
    <div class="scanlines"></div>
    <div class="game-card">
      <h1 class="game-hero text-4xl font-black mb-2 text-center">STATIC RUN</h1>
      <p class="tagline text-center mb-8">Run. Don't look back. The entropy fragments aren't chasing you — they're just waiting for you to stop.</p>

      <div class="specs">
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Genre</span><span>Endless Runner</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Engine</span><span>Godot 4</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Size</span><span>14.1 MB</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Season</span><span>2</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Character</span><span>Nano</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Price</span><span>Free forever</span></div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        Nano was an engineer on Cogsworth Cogitarium's frequency-hop program. She built the tuners that let ships jump between known frequencies. Good work. Precise work. Then a prototype jumped a survey vessel into a dead frequency. No survivors. The inquiry blamed her calculations. Her calculations were flawless. She resigned and went into the Space.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        The Ephergent found her four months later, running along the hull of a derelict Builder Station at a speed that should not have been possible for a human body. Pixel hailed her. Nano didn't slow down. She couldn't. She had been running for so long that standing still felt like dying.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        This game is about how long, not whether. You can always outrun them. The entropy fragments will never catch Nano if you keep moving. There is no death by catching. There is death by obstacle — by losing momentum, by hesitating, by slowing down long enough that the corridor collapses around you.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a href="/games/static-run/play/" class="nav-link font-bold">Play Now</a>
        <a href="/games/static-run/about/" class="nav-link">About</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
